The paper discusses the design and implementation of a mobile honeypot to analyze unsolicited traffic to and from mobile devices. This topic falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR) and networked systems (cs.NI). The paper also discusses the challenges of the mobile regime, which could fall under software engineering (cs.SE) and systems and control (cs.SY). Finally, the paper mentions the use of smartphones, which could fall under multimedia (cs.MM).
